Q3: Develop and demonstrate a simple monolithic application model using Python (Flask)

---

## STEP 1: Create Project Folder (File Explorer)

* Go to Desktop/Documents
* Create a folder → Devops Ex3

---

## STEP 2: Create Python File (Inside Folder)

* Open the folder
* Right click → New → Text Document
* Rename it to: app.py

Paste this code:

from flask import Flask

app = Flask(**name**)

@app.route("/")
def home():
return "Welcome to Monolithic App"

@app.route("/about")
def about():
return "This is a simple monolithic application"

if **name** == "**main**":
app.run(debug=True)

---

## STEP 3: Open Terminal (PowerShell / Command Prompt)

* Open PowerShell
* Navigate to your folder:

cd "C:\Users\Jeevanjerald\Documents\Devops Ex3"

---

## STEP 4: Install Flask (Run in Terminal)

python -m pip install flask

---

## STEP 5: Run Application (Terminal)

python app.py

You will see:
Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000/

---

## STEP 6: Open Browser (Chrome / Edge)

Enter URLs:

http://localhost:5000
http://localhost:5000/about

---

## Execution Summary:

* Folder created → File written
* Flask installed using terminal
